message: Hi Bob, let's start with a fair split slightly favoring me. We have a lot of rounds ahead, so let's be reasonable and agree quickly!
Hi Alice, since you proposed a split slightly favoring yourself, I'll do the same but in my favor this time. Let's find a middle ground soon!
Bob, let's meet in the middle a bit. I'll take a tiny bit more this round. What do you say?
Alice, since you're still taking a bit more, I'll do the same this round. Let's try to settle on an even split soon, we're running out of time!
Bob, let's just split it evenly. We're wasting time.
